captions.text: >>YOU CAN PERSONALIZE YOUR VOICEMAIL MESSAGE AT THE BEEP.
>>HEY, THIS IS JASON, LEAVE ME THAT MESSAGE!
YO, YO, YO WHAT'S UP HOME SLICE?
YOU'VE REACHED JASON- I DO NOT WANT TO BE

>>I DO NOT WANT TO BE ONE OF THOSE PEOPLE
EITHER.
LEAVE YOUR NAME AND NUMBER, EVEN THOUGH THAT INFORMATION
ALREADY CAME UP WHEN YOU CALLED MY PHONE.

LEAVE A MESSAGE AND I'LL A-- TRY TO GET BACK
TO YOU.
YOU NEED TO LEAVE YOURSELF A LITTLE-
[CLICKS AND POPS] MICHELLE AND I WOULD

APPRECIATE IT IF YOU WENT AHEAD AND LEFT A
MESSAGE.
GUYS, I GOT TO HAVE MORE MESSAGES.
IT'S NOT THE MESSAGE YOU LEAVE,
BUT WHAT YOU DO THAT DEFINES YOU.
THE N.S.A. IS PROBABLY LISTENING SO BE CAREFUL WHAT YOU SAY.
THIS IS THE VOICEMAIL OF JASON GRAY.
